{
  "stem": "23641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other hand, I tried to be [INAUDIBLE] for a living, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Become a ghetto because-- and all around the villages-- used to be a lot of Jewish people in those villages-- send them in in Wlodawa.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know really why Wlodawa became a ghetto, until when they built Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we knew that was the purpose for because Sobibor was only seven kilometers from our city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1941-- the end of 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they packed in all the people from the villages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They packed them in the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not enough room for everybody, so they had to squeeze in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some-- in some-- in some houses, they lived two peop-- ten people in some.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we had to squeeze it in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that's the best we could do, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't go out of the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to stay just inside, in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not go out-- out of the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you go out, you get killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course they were shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things like that-- sure, were shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you go out-- nobody tried to go out, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you go out, you-- they, they shoot you, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You stay in, you stay in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- do you want me to tell you the story what I heard with those-- with Falkenburg at Sobibor?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Falkenburg came to Wlodawa in 19-- in 194-- '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he established-- they called it the dry-- dry land.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we had a lot of wetland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came with idea to make the land dry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think-- I started to work for Falkenburg in 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the 19-- and then in winter, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went back to the tailor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
